{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":928,"text":"If you look deep into the night sky,"},{"time":4420,"text":"you see stars,"},{"time":6036,"text":"and if you look further, you see more stars,"},{"time":8608,"text":"and further, galaxies, and \nfurther, more galaxies."},{"time":10767,"text":"But if you keep looking further and further,"},{"time":14640,"text":"eventually you see nothing for a long while,"},{"time":17756,"text":"and then finally you see a\nfaint, fading afterglow,"},{"time":22218,"text":"and it's the afterglow of the Big Bang."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25242,"text":"Now, the Big Bang was an era in the early universe"},{"time":28059,"text":"when everything we see in the night sky"},{"time":30230,"text":"was condensed into an incredibly small,"},{"time":32640,"text":"incredibly hot, incredibly roiling mass,"},{"time":36966,"text":"and from it sprung everything we see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39658,"text":"Now, we've mapped that afterglow"},{"time":42517,"text":"with great precision,"},{"time":44196,"text":"and when I say we, I mean people who aren't me."},{"time":46240,"text":"We've mapped the afterglow"},{"time":48116,"text":"with spectacular precision,"},{"time":49438,"text":"and one of the shocks about it"},{"time":50986,"text":"is that it's almost completely uniform."},{"time":53932,"text":"Fourteen billion light years that way"},{"time":55890,"text":"and 14 billion light years that way,"},{"time":57750,"text":"it's the same temperature."},{"time":59158,"text":"Now it's been 14 billion years"},{"time":62472,"text":"since that Big Bang,"},{"time":64290,"text":"and so it's got faint and cold."},{"time":66762,"text":"It's now 2.7 degrees."},{"time":69070,"text":"But it's not exactly 2.7 degrees."},{"time":71350,"text":"It's only 2.7 degrees to about"},{"time":73644,"text":"10 parts in a million."},{"time":75486,"text":"Over here, it's a little hotter,"},{"time":76480,"text":"and over there, it's a little cooler,"},{"time":78348,"text":"and that's incredibly important\nto everyone in this room,"},{"time":81436,"text":"because where it was a little hotter,"},{"time":83160,"text":"there was a little more stuff,"},{"time":84856,"text":"and where there was a little more stuff,"},{"time":86423,"text":"we have galaxies and clusters of galaxies"},{"time":88392,"text":"and superclusters"},{"time":89644,"text":"and all the structure you see in the cosmos."},{"time":92352,"text":"And those small, little, inhomogeneities,"},{"time":95464,"text":"20 parts in a million,"},{"time":97746,"text":"those were formed by quantum mechanical wiggles"},{"time":100500,"text":"in that early universe that were stretched"},{"time":102308,"text":"across the size of the entire cosmos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104587,"text":"That is spectacular,"},{"time":106301,"text":"and that's not what they found on Monday;"},{"time":107966,"text":"what they found on Monday is cooler."},{"time":110002,"text":"So here's what they found on Monday:"},{"time":112268,"text":"Imagine you take a bell,"},{"time":115771,"text":"and you whack the bell with a hammer."},{"time":117382,"text":"What happens? It rings."},{"time":119058,"text":"But if you wait, that ringing fades"},{"time":121266,"text":"and fades and fades"},{"time":122886,"text":"until you don't notice it anymore."},{"time":124828,"text":"Now, that early universe was incredibly dense,"},{"time":127476,"text":"like a metal, way denser,"},{"time":129555,"text":"and if you hit it, it would ring,"},{"time":131960,"text":"but the thing ringing would be"},{"time":133823,"text":"the structure of space-time itself,"},{"time":135911,"text":"and the hammer would be quantum mechanics."},{"time":138727,"text":"What they found on Monday"},{"time":140658,"text":"was evidence of the ringing"},{"time":143020,"text":"of the space-time of the early universe,"},{"time":145335,"text":"what we call gravitational waves"},{"time":147440,"text":"from the fundamental era,"},{"time":148960,"text":"and here's how they found it."},{"time":150935,"text":"Those waves have long since faded."},{"time":153007,"text":"If you go for a walk,"},{"time":154495,"text":"you don't wiggle."},{"time":156083,"text":"Those gravitational waves in the structure of space"},{"time":158831,"text":"are totally invisible for all practical purposes."},{"time":161605,"text":"But early on, when the universe was making"},{"time":164509,"text":"that last afterglow,"},{"time":166879,"text":"the gravitational waves"},{"time":168437,"text":"put little twists in the structure"},{"time":171300,"text":"of the light that we see."},{"time":172827,"text":"So by looking at the night sky deeper and deeper --"},{"time":175793,"text":"in fact, these guys spent\nthree years on the South Pole"},{"time":178431,"text":"looking straight up through the coldest, clearest,"},{"time":181020,"text":"cleanest air they possibly could find"},{"time":183370,"text":"looking deep into the night sky and studying"},{"time":185799,"text":"that glow and looking for the faint twists"},{"time":189175,"text":"which are the symbol, the signal,"},{"time":191523,"text":"of gravitational waves,"},{"time":193343,"text":"the ringing of the early universe."},{"time":195684,"text":"And on Monday, they announced"},{"time":197471,"text":"that they had found it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199215,"text":"And the thing that's so spectacular about that to me"},{"time":201642,"text":"is not just the ringing, though that is awesome."},{"time":204390,"text":"The thing that's totally amazing,"},{"time":205748,"text":"the reason I'm on this stage, is because"},{"time":207850,"text":"what that tells us is something\ndeep about the early universe."},{"time":211318,"text":"It tells us that we"},{"time":212982,"text":"and everything we see around us"},{"time":214418,"text":"are basically one large bubble --"},{"time":217372,"text":"and this is the idea of inflationâ€”"},{"time":219128,"text":"one large bubble surrounded by something else."},{"time":223020,"text":"This isn't conclusive evidence for inflation,"},{"time":225150,"text":"but anything that isn't inflation that explains this"},{"time":227324,"text":"will look the same."},{"time":228641,"text":"This is a theory, an idea,"},{"time":230286,"text":"that has been around for a while,"},{"time":231510,"text":"and we never thought we we'd really see it."},{"time":233235,"text":"For good reasons, we thought we'd never see"},{"time":235073,"text":"killer evidence, and this is killer evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237321,"text":"But the really crazy idea"},{"time":239331,"text":"is that our bubble is just one bubble"},{"time":242363,"text":"in a much larger, roiling pot of universal stuff."},{"time":246989,"text":"We're never going to see the stuff outside,"},{"time":248815,"text":"but by going to the South Pole\nand spending three years"},{"time":251389,"text":"looking at the detailed structure of the night sky,"},{"time":253949,"text":"we can figure out"},{"time":255805,"text":"that we're probably in a universe\nthat looks kind of like that."},{"time":258895,"text":"And that amazes me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261317,"text":"Thanks a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262653,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}